    @Internal
public abstract class CommandOutputBus<M extends com.google.protobuf.Message,E extends io.spine.core.MessageEnvelope<?,M,?>,C extends io.spine.type.MessageClass,D extends MessageDispatcher<C,E,?>>
extends MulticastBus<M,E,C,D>
    A base bus responsible for delivering the command output.

    The typical output artifacts of the command processing are:

    • events — in case the command is handled successfully;
    • rejections — if the command contradicts the business rules.

    The instances of CommandOutputBus are responsible for a delivery of such output artifacts to the corresponding destinations.
